error_message: You have passed a tuple to the predict() function instead of a Numpy array or a Dict. You are probably mixing Gym API with SB3 VecEnv API: `obs, info = env.reset()` (Gym) vs `obs = vec_env.reset()` (SB3 VecEnv). See related issue https://github.com/DLR-RM/stable-baselines3/issues/1694 and documentation for more information: https://stable-baselines3.readthedocs.io/en/master/guide/vec_envs.html#vecenv-api-vs-gym-api
